  description="Digitale Kunst Angewandte Festival Diplomas Admission Team Schauraum Labs Contact|"
  showContact
  open
>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-yellow prose-headings:text-yellow marker:text-yellow prose-a:text-yellow !text-decoration:none"
  >
    <Container>

      <p>
        <h1>A riot tech approach to code, emotion, theory, flex, aesthetics. It’s not clean. It’s not quiet. But it’s real. And it works. We eat together, watch insurgency grow. The city bleeds into us. Survival becomes method. Non-contrarian soft contradiction, max impact. Digital art ain't discipline — it's ethics. </h1><br>
      </p>
     
      <p>
          <a href="/af" class="font-bold no-underline"­> 
            <h1>Meet us at the Angewandte Festival! <br/> June 25th - 28th 2025 </h1>
          </a>
      </p>
       <p>
        <a href="/af" class="font-bold no-underline"­> 
        <h1> ANDY KASSIER: Identity as a game - Open Lecture is coming up <br/>
               June 26th - 2025, 2pm, Immersive Lab at DK </h1>
        </a>
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/chasing-echoes-and-taming-machines" class="font-bold no-underline">
          <h1>
            Drop by at the Screening "Chasing Echoes and Taming Machines"
            Blickle Kino, Belvedere <br/> 21 April 27th 2025, 12:00 - 13:45
          </h1>
        </a>
      </p>
    </Container>
